2026-05-14T04:03:11.3406934Z 13    <!--
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3408003Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3408854Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3410204Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3411043Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3411913Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3412602Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
