2026-05-14T04:03:11.3416670Z 22    <!--
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3417246Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3417967Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3418636Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3449726Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3450524Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3451323Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3452381Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3453089Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3453762Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3454399Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3454894Z 33    -->
2026-05-14T04:03:11.3455441Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
